channel.title: Have some problems
channel.description:
Hello people,
I'm not a very good coder. So .. I have some problems and hope I can get it solved quickly.

Then I port forward with uTorrent, no-ip created and put into client Ip, (how you put your ip in your source?) But I can not continue to the Web client to make it run. By the way, I use that as a test to see if my server is online. So ... What am I doing wrong? Does anyone know?
[b][i][u]Sorry for if my English is not good. I grew up is not a British national.[/u][/i][/b]

I also do not really problems, but if what is being changed topic.
